welcome_finami_start: Let's start with the first steps towards better financial health.
know_who_is_start: To start, we need to know who you are.
welcome_message: Once this is done, it's important that you help us organize your financial information by entering a first account. This will allow the system to gather the records in one place, giving you a clear view of your financial movements. You will be able to modify this data in the “Accounts” section.
welcome_caution: We want to assure you that your information is safe with us, only you will have access to it.
delete_account_subtitle: We're sorry to see you go.
delete_account_body: To confirm the deletion of your account, please enter your username in the box below.
delete_account_warning: Please note that this action is irreversible. Once your account is deleted, all your data will be permanently removed from our system.
camera_permission: In order to use the Camera, you'll need to allow this App access to it

welcome_beta: Welcome to our beta version app!
welcome_beta_text01: We want to share with you that this app is still under development and we are working hard to improve it every day. We value your opinion and would like you to help us make this app the best experience for you.
welcome_beta_text02: During this testing phase, we are especially interested in receiving feedback and suggestions for improvement. We have included a section in the menu called "Leave Us Your Feedback" where you can rate and share your ideas about the app.
welcome_beta_text03: Your participation is crucial to us. We would like to know what you like, what you find confusing, or any area that you believe needs improvement. Your feedback will help us identify and solve problems, as well as add new features that are important to you.
welcome_beta_text04: We want to thank you for being part of our evolutionary process. Thank you for your patience and for contributing to making this app an even better tool.

leave_comments_1: We are glad that you are interested in helping us improve our application. We want you to have the best possible experience, so your feedback and suggestions are very important to us.
leave_comments_2: Please take a moment to share your ideas, issues, or any other observations you have about the application. Your opinion is crucial for us to continue moving forward.
leave_comments_3: If you encounter any bugs or errors, please describe them in detail so that we can fix them as soon as possible. You can also attach screenshots if necessary.
leave_comments_4: We are excited to hear from you and keep improving together.
leave_comments_5: Thank you for being part of our growth process!
